&lt;p&gt;The teams currently hiring are described below.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;To learn more about automation engineering at Ginkgo, please visit&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.ginkgo.bio/product/software&quot;&gt; our website&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
