&lt;li&gt;Improve scheduler quality (utilization, throughput, latency) and robustness against partial failures and live perturbations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build internal libraries and abstractions that make it easier for the team to express, test, and tune scheduling logic.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
