&lt;div class=&quot;p-rich_text_section&quot;&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;p-rich_text_section&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;The base salary range for this role is $45,100-$63,600. Actual pay within this range will depend on a candidate&#39;s skills, expertise, and experience. We also offer a comprehensive benefits package including medical, dental &amp;amp; vision coverage, health spending accounts, voluntary benefits, leave of absence policies, 8 paid holidays in addition to a full-week winter shutdown and unlimited Paid Time Off policy.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;*It is expected that all Internships are onsite five days a week.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
